THav2m0G_CXFVLhI8X5V5H5WV0w%3Dh900-rw&h=310d0676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/x5280G_ZCGdWBhyvr_1CUft8X4ynjDFitnv9dASa-pFcxQG__kcpRKgz9vgPgSNRmQ=h900-rw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fx5280G_ZCGdWBhyvr_1CUft8X4ynjDFitnv9dASa-pFcxQG__kcpRKgz9vgPgSNRmQ%3Dh900-rw&h=736f557d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-dbQXPLjGwjyGa55NDazLCIzEs_2LM75ffrsrl_3CRPNh6BzlOQPhqw0Mp2hBDp867yt=h900-rw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2F-dbQXPLjGwjyGa55NDazLCIzEs_2LM75ffrsrl_3CRPNh6BzlOQPhqw0Mp2hBDp867yt%3Dh900-rw&h=8d8fb5db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/YWhiHskO1-FFyILfb1z1vtqRJkg2-gq726lgzyNN291R3_X9q6GEW0ZwKUWSd09PdA=h900-rw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FYWhiHskO1-FFyILfb1z1vtqRJkg2-gq726lgzyNN291R3_X9q6GEW0ZwKUWSd09PdA%3Dh900-rw&h=590cb4a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10分鐘一局，線上最佳吃雞手遊！《Free Fire - 我要活下去》是一款大逃殺類型的荒島生存射擊遊戲。運輸機掠過荒島，數十名玩家自由跳傘，四散於荒島進行求生！電磁圈危機逐漸逼近，你只有想辦法活下去！駕駛載具狂飆於荒野中，在廣闊地圖中探索生存的機會，埋伏、狙擊一觸即發！目標只有一個：我要活下去！成為最後的倖存者！<br />\n<br />\n【全新戰隊 一同吃雞】<br />\n組建最強戰隊，與戰隊成員一起共赴戰場！<br />\n<br />\n【原汁原味 生存遊戲】<br />\n高自由度場景，戰局隨時改變。電磁侵襲、搜刮資源、潛伏偷襲、掠奪戰利品、空襲轟炸、絕境逆襲，活到最後就是強者，還原絕境生存經典玩法。<br />\n<br />\n【荒島試煉 最終考驗】<br />\n每局50人的快節奏激戰，10分鐘的激戰中選擇躲藏還是勇敢向前，你的生存之道由你自己決定！<br />\n<br />\n【即時語音 四人組隊】<br />\n遊戲內建小隊語音系統，支持雙人和四人模式。與你的好友一起組隊求生，更支持 Facebook 好友組隊，一鍵邀請，馬上行動。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有冇人玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</span>"},{"pid":"7cde4072ca9196b5136d05aeb1c7b51e9f48a1eb","tid":574193,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T07:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729d2c2b7701be8bfd8159f9d97242a4f960267e","tid":574193,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,